<L>__{interior steeple day}
<A>__{bell ropes, hundreds of feet long, dangle down the vertiginous shaft. d'artagnan races up the narrow, circular stairs. above him is the open trap to the bell tower. he catches a glimpse of the marksman, back turned, taking aim.}
