<B>__{in crowd below}
<A>__{athos, porthos, and aramis push their way through the crowd, trying desperately to reach the palace entrance. but the throng is impenetrable. athos turns, wonders. and shoots a worried look at the bell tower of the carmes deschaux, looming against the sky, as if to intuit the danger lurking there.}
